        "json_string": "[\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Hugging from behind at the shoreline\",\n    \"prompt\": \"A 17 year old woman with long brown hair and blue eyes stands barefoot at the shoreline, watching the horizon, waves gently lapping at her ankles. An 18 year old man with short black hair and green eyes wraps his arms around her from behind, resting his chin on her shoulder. She\u2019s wearing a breezy sundress, and he\u2019s in his black hoodie and rolled-up jeans. Shot from the side, golden light catching the edge of the water, their silhouettes close.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Writing names in the sand\",\n    \"prompt\": \"A 17 year old woman with long brown hair and blue eyes kneels in the sand with a stick, carefully writing her name beside the name of an 18 year old man with short black hair and green eyes. She wears a striped tank top and cutoff shorts. He stands nearby, watching with a smile, hoodie off and slung over his shoulder. Shot from above, the wet sand catching the reflection of their figures in the afternoon sun.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Dancing barefoot on the sand\",\n    \"prompt\": \"A 17 year old woman with long brown hair and blue eyes dances barefoot on the beach with an 18 year old man with short black hair and green eyes. She twirls in a light dress, laughing, while he holds one of her hands, off balance but grinning. He\u2019s still in his hoodie and jeans, pant legs wet from the tide. Shot wide, low sun casting long shadows and painting the scene in warm orange tones.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Sitting in a hammock together\",\n    \"prompt\": \"A 17 year old woman with long brown hair and blue eyes and an 18 year old man with short black hair and green eyes sit tangled together in a hammock strung between two palm trees near the shore. She wears a light cotton romper, her head resting on his chest, while he lazily pushes the hammock with one foot, hoodie hood up. Shot from the side, gentle sway visible, ocean blurred in the background.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Walking with a sparkler at dusk\",\n    \"prompt\": \"A 17 year old woman with long brown hair and blue eyes walks barefoot through the sand holding a lit sparkler, her other hand clasped with an 18 year old man with short black hair and green eyes. She wears a tank top and frayed shorts, the sparks lighting up her face. He walks beside her in his hoodie, watching the light trail. Shot at twilight, sea behind them fading into night.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Blowing bubbles at the beach\",\n    \"prompt\": \"A 17 year old woman with long brown hair and blue eyes sits cross-legged in the sand blowing bubbles while an 18 year old man with short black hair and green eyes tries to pop them mid-air. She wears a soft graphic tee and shorts, hair tucked behind her ears. He\u2019s barefoot, laughing, hoodie sleeves pushed up. Shot low to the sand, bubbles glinting in the light, horizon blurred behind them.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Sharing watermelon\",\n    \"prompt\": \"A 17 year old woman with long brown hair and blue eyes offers a slice of watermelon to an 18 year old man with short black hair and green eyes, both sitting under a beach umbrella. She\u2019s in a bikini top and a sarong, he\u2019s shirtless for once, hoodie hanging on the umbrella pole. Shot medium close-up, juice dripping from the fruit as they both laugh, sunlight filtering through the umbrella above.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Sitting in tide pools\",\n    \"prompt\": \"A 17 year old woman with long brown hair and blue eyes sits with her legs in a tide pool, searching for shells with an 18 year old man with short black hair and green eyes beside her. She wears rolled-up overalls and a swimsuit underneath, hair wet and messy. He has his hoodie off, tied around his waist. Shot from overhead, the water clear, small crabs and shells visible around them.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Whispering secrets\",\n    \"prompt\": \"A 17 year old woman with long brown hair and blue eyes leans in to whisper something to an 18 year old man with short black hair and green eyes, both crouched behind a sand dune. She\u2019s giggling, in a lightweight cardigan and shorts. He listens, smiling, hoodie sleeves rolled. Shot tight, with tall dune grass partially obscuring the frame, giving a feeling of intimacy.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Sunset piggyback ride\",\n    \"prompt\": \"An 18 year old man with short black hair and green eyes gives a piggyback ride to a 17 year old woman with long brown hair and blue eyes along the shoreline. She wears a sunhat and a light summer dress, arms around his neck, hair blowing in the wind. He\u2019s laughing, hoodie hanging off one shoulder. Shot wide from behind, with the orange sun dipping into the ocean, casting their long shadows on the wet sand.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Chasing each other in the shallow waves\",\n    \"prompt\": \"A 17 year old woman with long brown hair and blue eyes runs barefoot through the shallow waves, laughing as an 18 year old man with short black hair and green eyes chases her. She wears a flowing tank top over her bikini, while he\u2019s in rolled-up jeans, hoodie sleeves pushed up. Shot from the side at mid-distance, water splashing around their feet as the golden sunset glows behind them.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Building a sandcastle together\",\n    \"prompt\": \"A 17 year old woman with long brown hair and blue eyes kneels in the sand with an 18 year old man with short black hair and green eyes, working on an elaborate sandcastle. She wears a polka dot one-piece swimsuit and a sunhat, while he\u2019s shirtless, hoodie on the ground nearby. Shot from overhead, the intricate towers of the sandcastle framed by their focused expressions and sandy hands.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Lying side by side under a beach towel\",\n    \"prompt\": \"A 17 year old woman with long brown hair and blue eyes and an 18 year old man with short black hair and green eyes lie side by side under a striped beach towel, faces close. She\u2019s in a swimsuit, he\u2019s in his hoodie and shorts, both damp from a swim. Shot close-up from above, their noses nearly touching as they smile under the soft shadow of the towel, beach scattered around them.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Trying to fly a kite\",\n    \"prompt\": \"An 18 year old man with short black hair and green eyes runs with a colorful kite while a 17 year old woman with long brown hair and blue eyes holds the spool, laughing. She\u2019s in a denim skirt and crop top, barefoot in the sand. He\u2019s focused, hoodie flapping as he runs. Shot wide with the kite just catching wind, waves crashing in the distance and seagulls flying past.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Eating ice cream on the pier\",\n    \"prompt\": \"A 17 year old woman with long brown hair and blue eyes and an 18 year old man with short black hair and green eyes sit on a wooden pier, legs dangling over the edge as they eat melting ice cream. She wears a vintage-style summer dress and sandals, while he\u2019s in a hoodie and khaki shorts. Shot from behind, with the ocean stretching out in front of them and soft light reflecting on the water.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Resting in a beach tent\",\n    \"prompt\": \"A 17 year old woman with long brown hair and blue eyes naps with her head on the shoulder of an 18 year old man with short black hair and green eyes inside a pop-up beach tent. She\u2019s wrapped in a towel, he\u2019s reading a paperback book, hoodie partially zipped. Shot from the tent\u2019s opening, framing their peaceful expressions as waves roll in behind them.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Wading out into the sea hand in hand\",\n    \"prompt\": \"A 17 year old woman with long brown hair and blue eyes and an 18 year old man with short black hair and green eyes walk hand in hand into the sea, backs to camera. She\u2019s in a white swim top and floral shorts, he\u2019s in black swim trunks, hoodie discarded on the beach. Shot low from behind, water sparkling around them as they move deeper into the surf.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Sleeping under the stars\",\n    \"prompt\": \"A 17 year old woman with long brown hair and blue eyes lies beside an 18 year old man with short black hair and green eyes on a beach blanket, both gazing at the stars. She\u2019s wearing a zip-up hoodie and pajama shorts, he\u2019s in his usual black hoodie. Shot from above, with the faint outline of the sea in the darkness and stars densely filling the sky.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Canoeing along the coast\",\n    \"prompt\": \"A 17 year old woman with long brown hair and blue eyes and an 18 year old man with short black hair and green eyes paddle a small canoe along the rocky coast. She wears a bucket hat and athletic top, he\u2019s in his hoodie, concentrating on the oar. Shot from a drone overhead, the turquoise water clear and calm, shadows of the canoe visible on the sea floor.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Taking polaroids of each other\",\n    \"prompt\": \"A 17 year old woman with long brown hair and blue eyes points a vintage polaroid camera at an 18 year old man with short black hair and green eyes, who strikes a goofy pose on the sand. She\u2019s in overalls over a bikini, he\u2019s got his hoodie tied around his waist. Shot at an angle where we see the photo being taken, the joy and spontaneity captured in the warm coastal light.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Watching fireworks on the beach\",\n    \"prompt\": \"A 17 year old woman with long brown hair and blue eyes leans her head on the shoulder of an 18 year old man with short black hair and green eyes as fireworks burst overhead. She wears a light cardigan over her dress, and he\u2019s in his black hoodie and jeans. Shot from behind, both silhouetted against the night sky lit by colorful explosions, their hands linked in the sand.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Holding hands in a hammock\",\n    \"prompt\": \"A 17 year old woman with long brown hair and blue eyes lies side by side in a hammock with an 18 year old man with short black hair and green eyes. She wears a tank top and soft shorts, and he\u2019s in a thin hoodie and joggers. Shot close-up, their intertwined hands rest on her stomach as the hammock sways slightly with palm trees and sea breeze in the background.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Sitting on the lifeguard tower at sunset\",\n    \"prompt\": \"A 17 year old woman with long brown hair and blue eyes sits beside an 18 year old man with short black hair and green eyes on a lifeguard tower, both legs dangling. She\u2019s barefoot in a tied-up shirt and bikini bottoms, he\u2019s in his black hoodie and board shorts. Shot wide from below, capturing the tall tower silhouetted against a vivid orange sky and soft ripples of the sea.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Riding bikes along the coast\",\n    \"prompt\": \"A 17 year old woman with long brown hair and blue eyes laughs as she rides a mint-colored cruiser bike alongside an 18 year old man with short black hair and green eyes. She wears a knotted t-shirt and skirt, he\u2019s pedaling in his hoodie and shorts. Shot at mid-distance with ocean cliffs in the background, the late afternoon sun casting long shadows on the sand-covered boardwalk.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Slow dancing on the beach at dusk\",\n    \"prompt\": \"A 17 year old woman with long brown hair and blue eyes dances slowly with an 18 year old man with short black hair and green eyes on the wet sand, waves softly lapping nearby. She\u2019s barefoot in a sundress, he\u2019s in his black hoodie and rolled-up jeans. Shot from a distance with glowing string lights from a nearby beach hut in the background, capturing their quiet, private moment.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Picking seashells together\",\n    \"prompt\": \"A 17 year old woman with long brown hair and blue eyes crouches down beside an 18 year old man with short black hair and green eyes, both combing through the sand for seashells. She\u2019s wearing a tank top and denim shorts, he\u2019s in his hoodie with sleeves rolled up. Shot low to the ground, close-up of their hands sifting through shells, seafoam in the background.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Blowing bubbles in the wind\",\n    \"prompt\": \"A 17 year old woman with long brown hair and blue eyes blows bubbles from a small wand while an 18 year old man with short black hair and green eyes watches her, smiling. She\u2019s in a yellow dress, barefoot in the sand, he\u2019s beside her in a hoodie and shorts. Shot close-up with bubbles floating toward the camera, light reflecting in soft pastels against the sea and sky.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Writing names in the sand\",\n    \"prompt\": \"A 17 year old woman with long brown hair and blue eyes and an 18 year old man with short black hair and green eyes kneel side by side, writing their names in the sand with a stick. She\u2019s in a tie-front blouse and bathing suit bottoms, he\u2019s in a hoodie and cargo shorts. Shot from above, the letters bold in the wet sand as waves approach slowly in the distance.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Drinking smoothies under an umbrella\",\n    \"prompt\": \"A 17 year old woman with long brown hair and blue eyes sips a smoothie from a colorful cup beside an 18 year old man with short black hair and green eyes under a striped beach umbrella. She wears oversized sunglasses and a bikini top with a loose shirt, he\u2019s in his black hoodie with the hood down. Shot close-up, their relaxed smiles framed by bright fabric and sunlit beach vibes.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Running through beach grass\",\n    \"prompt\": \"A 17 year old woman with long brown hair and blue eyes runs barefoot through tall beach grass with an 18 year old man with short black hair and green eyes chasing after her. She wears a flowing sundress, and he\u2019s in his signature hoodie and shorts. Shot wide with a shallow depth of field, golden light streaming through the grass as laughter fills the air.\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"title\": \"Sunbathing together on the beach\",\n    \"prompt\": \"A 17 year old woman with long brown hair and blue eyes lies on a beach towel, sunbathing, wearing a white bikini and large sunglasses. Next to her, an 18 year old man with short black hair and green eyes reclines on his towel in a pair of board shorts and sunglasses. The sun casts a warm glow on them as they both smile, with the ocean gently rolling in the background. Shot from above, capturing the expansive beach and their peaceful, relaxed moment together.\"\n  }\n]\n",
